# ML models (too large for git, exported via `python -m data_classifier.export_onnx`)
# The Phase 2 meta-classifier artifacts are small (~8 KB combined) and
# committed per decision D5 — everything else in this directory is
# ignored by default.
data_classifier/models/*
!data_classifier/models/__init__.py
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v1.pkl
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v1.metadata.json
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v1.eval.json
# Research candidate artifacts from parallel experiments (meta-classifier queue).
# Same size class as v1; see docs/experiments/meta_classifier/queue.md file-ownership.
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v1_*.pkl
!data_classifier/models/meta_classifier_v1_*.metadata.json
models/gliner_onnx/
